r />\n<br />\n她向《立場新聞》承認已離職，又打趣說「Wiki （維基百科）唔啱，我係尋日正式遞信。」她說離職是私人原因，著記者向警察公共關係科查詢，但笑說「PPRB 講嘅嘢我都唔回應啦。」她說對於離職心情放鬆，會準備未來的日子，又說自己一直關注動物權益，「可能你無睇《警訊》，之前都做好多動物專題」，她又表示，現時正聯絡動物權益機構，「希望大眾可以多啲 focus （關注）動物權益。」<br />\n<br />\n任職警察 6 年，梁皓妤說最不捨的是曾經共事的「戰友」，「包括《警訊》的團隊，演員、導演、警察同事。」但她說會向前望，「又唔係唔見，都會出嚟食飯嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n在警民關係惡劣的現在，作為一名較受歡迎的警察，臨別有寄語嗎？「唔好咁講，唔係受歡迎，只係畀人起咗底咋。」她想了一會後說，「大家唔好有仇恨。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%82%B3%E5%9B%A0%E6%94%BF%E8%A6%8B%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%BF%E9%9B%A2-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%8A-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81-%E5%B7%B2%E5%9B%A0-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E9%81%9E%E4%BF%A1%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E9%259B%25A2-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E9%2581%259E%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=a65c5a6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E9%259B%25A2-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E9%2581%259E%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E8%2581%25B7%2F&h=1efa2470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%82%B3%E5%9B%A0%E6%94%BF%E8%A6%8B%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%BF%E9%9B%A2-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%8A-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81-%E5%B7%B2%E5%9B%A0-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E9%81%9E%E4%BF%A1%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0